	<string key="N3000003" ger="Dual Mastery" eng="Dual Mastery" />
	<string key="T3000003" ger="Ein passiver Skill, dessen Wirkung eintritt, sobald das Item angelegt wird. HP ist um +20 und SP um +20 erhöht, so dass man in verschiedensten Situationen leicht reagieren kann." eng="It's one of passive skills and if you equip it, the item effects are activated. Both HP+20 and SP+20 are increased, so you can easily react against various situations." />
