	<string key="N4050366" ger="Surfingboard Anchoring Capsule" eng="Surfingboard Anchoring Capsule" />
	<string key="T4050366" ger="Mit dieser Capsule kannst du den Surfingboard Anchoring Skill bekommen.{N}Wenn du diese Capsule benutzt, hast du die Chance, folgende Items zu gewinnen: {N}{CB-255,255,0,255}Surfingboard Anchoring (permanent/SP-Verbrauch -5%/Reichweite +5%){N}Surfingboard Anchoring (7Tage/SP-Verbrauch -5%/Reichweite +5%){N}Surfingboard Anchoring (30Tage/SP-Verbrauch -5%/Reichweite +5%)" eng="With this Capsule, you might able to earn the surfingboard achoring skill. {N}If the Capsule is used, you will have the chance to win the item below. {N}{CB-255,255,0,255}Surfing Board Anchoring (Permanent/ SP usage -5%, Range increased by +5%){N}Surfingboard Anchoring (7 days/ SP Usage -5%, Range increased by +5%){N} Surfingboard Anchoring (30 days/ SP usage -5%, Range increased by +5%)" />
	<string key="N2010035" ger="Golden Gear Smash Rifle" eng="Golden Gear Smash Rifle" />
	<string key="T2010035" ger="Diese Smash Rifle wird von Detektiven benutzt. Die goldenen Reflektoren erhellen selbst die dunkelsten Orte." eng="A Smash Rifle that has been originally used by an adventurer in S4. The reflected light from the Smash Rifle helps the adventurers when they explore in the darkness." />
