	<string key="T4035255" ger="Halloween Gift Box. Öffne die Box, um zu sehen, was darin ist!" eng="Halloween Gift Box. Open the box and see what's inside!" />
	<string key="N4035256" ger="Death Impactor Set Capsule" eng="Death Impactor Set Capsule" />
	<string key="T4035256" ger="Mit dieser Capsule hast du die Chance, das Death Impactor Costume Set zu erhalten.{N} Das Set enthält folgende Items:" eng="Death Impactor Costume Set can be acquired.{N} Use this Capsule item and you will receive some of the following items randomly." />
	<string key="N4035257" ger="Death Queen Set Capsule" eng="Death Queen Set Capsule" />
	<string key="T4035257" ger="Mit dieser Capsule hast du die Chance, das Death Queen Costume Set zu erhalten.{N} Das Set enthält folgende Items:" eng="Death Queen Costume Set can be acquired.{N} Use this Capsule item and you will receive some of the following items randomly." />
	<string key="N4035258" ger="Death Scythe of Skeleton Capsule" eng="Death Scythe of Skeleton Capsule" tha="Death Scythe of Skeleton Capsule"/>
	<string key="T4035258" ger="Death Scythe of Skeleton Capsule Capsule{N}Wenn du diese Capsule öffnest, erhältst du aus jeder Kategorie ein zufällig ausgewähltes Item." eng="The Death Scythe of Skeleton Capsule.{N}The Death Scythe of Skeleton weapon can be acquired. Use this Capsule and you will receive some of the following items randomly." />
	<string key="N4035259" ger="Scorpio Pet Capsule" eng="Scorpio pet Capsule" />
	<string key="T4035259" ger="Ein riesiger Skorpion, der Orion zu Tode gestochen hat! Schau, ob du ihn zu deinem treuen Begleiter machen kannst." eng="A huge scorpion which stung Orion to death! See if you can own this loyal pet." />
	<string key="N4035260" ger="Fifth Secret Girl - Ophelia" eng="Fifth Secret Girl - Ophelia" />
