	<string key="N4051332" ger="Wings of Death Capsule" eng="Wings of Death Capsule" />
	<string key="T4051332" ger="Mit dieser Capsule hast du die Chance, Wings Of Death zu erhalten. {N} Wenn du diese Capsule benutzt, erhältst du ein zufällig ausgewähltes Item aus folgender Liste:{N}{CB-255,255,0,255}Wings Of Death (permanent/-5% SP-Verbrauch, +10% Movement Speed){N}Wings Of Death (7Tage/-5% SP-Verbrauch, +10% Movement Speed){N}Wings Of Death (30Tage/-5% SP-Verbrauch, +10% Movement Speed)" eng="Wings Of Death Skill can be acquired. Use this Capsule item and you will receive some of the following items randomly.{N}{CB-255,255,0,255}Wings Of Death (Permanent / SP usage -5%, MoveSpeed +10%), {N}Wings Of Death (7 Days / SP usage -5%, MoveSpeed +10%), {N}Wings Of Death (30 Days / SP usage -5%, MoveSpeed +10%)." />
