	<string key="T4035305" ger="Lilian's Lovebird with items.{N}Use this capsule and you will receive the following items." eng="Lilian's Lovebird with items.{N}Use this capsule and you will receive the following items." />
	<string key="N4020029" ger="[EVENT] Item Crafting Experiential Kit" eng="[EVENT] Item Crafting Experiential Kit" />
	<string key="T4020029" ger="Item Dismentling/Crafting Experiential Kit.{N}Use this kit, you will receive items for crafting Gauss Rifle MK2(1day)." eng="Item Dismentling/Crafting Experiential Kit.{N}Use this kit, you will receive items for crafting Gauss Rifle MK2(1day)." />
	<string key="N4020035" ger="Crafting Elements Capsule(Light)" eng="Crafting Elements Capsule(Light)" />
	<string key="T4020035" ger="Crafting Elements Capsule.{N}Diese Capsule enthält folgende Items:{CB-0,255,0,255}{N}{N}Du erhältst ein zufällig ausgewähltes Element für den Bat Rabbit." eng="Crafting elements capsule.{N}Use this capsule and you will receive the following items.{CB-0,255,0,255}{N}{N}You can receive a Bat Rabbit Piece randomly." />
	<string key="N4020030" ger="Male Face-off Capsule" eng="Male Face-off Capsule" />
	<string key="T4020030" ger="Capsule for 3 kinds of male face.{N}Use this capsule and you will receive one of the following items randomly." eng="Capsule for 3 kinds of male face.{N}Use this capsule and you will receive one of the following items randomly." />
	<string key="N4020031" ger="Female Face-off Capsule" eng="Female Face-off Capsule" />
	<string key="T4020031" ger="Capsule for 3 kinds of female face.{N}Use this capsule and you will receive one of the following items randomly." eng="Capsule for 3 kinds of female face.{N}Use this capsule and you will receive one of the following items randomly." />
	<string key="N6010005" ger="Bat Rabbit Piece" eng="Bat Rabbit Piece" />
	<string key="T6010005" ger="Limitiertes Element für den Bat Rabbit, mit dem die Einführung der Itemherstellung und -zerlegung gefeiert wird.{N}{N}Benutze dieses Item, um die limitierte Edition des Super Bat Rabbit herzustellen." eng="Limited edition of Bat Rabbit Piece to celebrate the implementation of the item dismantling/crafting system.{N}{N}Use this to craft the limited edition of Stormbat Rabbit. At the end of the event, all Bat Rabbit pieces will be removed." />
	<string key="N4035307" ger="G's Gauss Rifle MK2 Capsule" eng="G's Gauss Rifle MK2 Capsule" />
	<string key="T4035307" ger="Gauss Rifle MK2 inklusive Items.{N}Benutze diese Capsule, um folgende Zufallsitems zu erhalten:" eng="Gauss Rifle MK2 with items.{N}Use this capsule and you will receive the following items randomly." />
	<string key="N2020010" ger="Rocket Launcher" eng="Rocket Launcher" />
	<string key="T2020010" ger="Der Rocket Launcher wurde von einer ominösen Hackergruppe namens Mad 'M' entwickelt. Schnelle Raketensalven oder konzentrierte Feuerstöße – Diese Waffe kann haut richtig rein! Dazu kommen noch spezielle Sonderfunktionen - typisch Mad 'M' eben." eng="Newly invented weapon by enigmatic hacker group, Mad 'M', of S4 League. Can use for rapid fires and a big strong shot. Also, has various special functions according to the style of Mad 'M'." />
	<string key="N2020011" ger="Rocket Launcher By Mad 'M'" eng="Rocket Launcher by Mad 'M'" />
	<string key="T2020011" ger="Ein Rocket Launcher mit einem Upgrade von Mad 'M'. Er ist größer und hat mehr Feuerkraft. Er funktioniert mit Zwei-Schritt-Kompression und garantiert somit mehr Action. Außerdem hat die Waffe viele Spezialfunktionen - typisch Mad 'M' eben!" eng="A Rocket Launcher upgraded by Mad 'M'. It's bigger and comes with more firepower. It uses a two-step compression, allowing for actioned-packed control. It also has lots of special functions, just the way Mad 'M' likes it." />
	<string key="N7028005" />
	<string key="T7028005" />
	<string key="N1070058" ger="Peony Parrot" eng="Peony Parrot" />
	<string key="T1070058" ger="A lovely peony parrot. It follows you whispering sweet nothings in your ear." eng="Ein hübscher Papagei. Er krächzt dir liebevoll ins Ohr." />
	<string key="N4020036" ger="Crafting Elements Capsule" eng="Crafting Elements Capsule" />
	<string key="T4020036" ger="Crafting Elements Capsule.{N}Diese Capsule enthält folgende Items:{CB-0,255,0,255}{N}{N}Du erhältst ein zufällig ausgewähltes Element für den Bat Rabbit." eng="Crafting elements capsule.{N}Use this capsule and you will receive the following items.{CB-0,255,0,255}{N}{N}You can receive a Bat Rabbit Piece randomly." />
