	<string key="T2020040" ger="Neu hergestellte und verbesserte Gauss Rifle MK2. Mit dieser Waffe rockst du die Netsphere!" eng="Newly created Gauss Rifle MK2. Occupy Net Sphere with upgraded Gauss Rifle MK2." jap="Newly created Gauss Rifle MK2. Occupy Net Sphere with upgraded Gauss Rifle MK2."/>
