	<string key="T4051881" eng="A complete C's Sailor Girl set. {N} Set contains the following items:" />
	<string key="N1001158" ger="Hardcore Mohawk Hair" eng="Intense Mohawk" />
	<string key="T1001158" ger="Mit diesem krassen Iro zeigst du klar, was du vom Establishment hältst!" eng="A badass mohawk that defines the punk spirit." />
	<string key="N1021158" ger="Punk Rock Studded Jacket" eng="Punk Rock Studded Jacket" />
	<string key="T1021158" ger="Biker-Jacke mit glänzenden Nieten und Schnallen." eng="A biker jacket studded with spikes and buckles." />
	<string key="N1031158" ger="Punk Rock Crest Pants" eng="Punk Rock Pants" />
	<string key="T1031158" ger="Schnallenhose mit Karomuster und Taschen." eng="Show the world your rebellious streak with these buckle-studded checkered pants." />
	<string key="N1041158" ger="Punk Rock Buckle Gloves" eng="Punk Rock Gloves" />
	<string key="T1041158" ger="Abgefahrene Handschuhe mit Schnallen und Nieten." eng="These leather gloves are decked out with buckles and metal studs." />
	<string key="N1051158" ger="Punk Rock Buckle Boots" eng="Punk Rock Buckle Boots" />
	<string key="T1051158" ger="Robuste Schnallenstiefel für festen Tritt." eng="Buckled biker boots that show off your punk attitude." />
	<string key="N1001159" ger="Side Cornrows" eng="Side Cornrows" />
	<string key="T1001159" ger="Die Cornrows verleihen deiner Bobfrisur das punkige Etwas." eng="Short bob hairstyle with cornrows for an iconoclastic look." />
	<string key="N1021159" ger="Valley Rose Corset" eng="Valley Rose Corset" />
	<string key="T1021159" ger="Corsage im Lagenlook mit punkiger Krawatte." eng="A layered corset with a punky tie." />
	<string key="N1031159" ger="Valley Rose Buckle Skirt" eng="Valley Rose Buckle Skirt" />
	<string key="T1031159" ger="Ein asymmetrischer Rock mit Strumpfhalter." eng="An asymmetrical checkered skirt, complete with a garter belt to finish the look." />
	<string key="N1041159" ger="Valley Rose Gloves" eng="Valley Rose Gloves" />
	<string key="T1041159" ger="Lederhandschuhe mit Stofffetzen und Nieten." eng="Leather gloves with silk patches and metal studs." />
	<string key="N1051159" ger="Valley Rose Buckle Boots" eng="Valley Rose Buckle Boots" />
	<string key="T1051159" ger="Robuste Schnallenstiefel für festen Tritt." eng="Buckled biker boots that show off your punk attitude." />
