	<string key="N4035373" ger="G's Summer Night Mine Gun Capsule" eng="G's Summer Night Mine Gun Capsule" />
	<string key="T4035373" ger="Diese Kapsel enthält die Summer Night Mine Gun.{N}Kann folgende zufällige Items enthalten:" eng="A capsule containing a Summer Night Mine Gun.{N}The capsule contains the following random items:" />
	<string key="N4060105" ger="I's Black Grenade Capsule" eng="I's Black Grenade Capsule" />
	<string key="T4060105" ger="Diese Kapsel enthält eine Black Grenade.{N}Kann folgende Items enthalten:" eng="A capsule containing a Black Grenade.{N}The capsule contains the following items at random:" />
	<string key="N1001170" ger="Net Shaman Luna M Wild Style" eng="Net Shaman Luna M Wild Style" />
	<string key="T1001170" ger="Security Android Net Shaman's Hairstyle (Male){N}Niemand kann der Eleganz eines Mannes von Welt wiederstehen, dessen Haar in diesem pinken Farbton erstrahlt!" eng="Security Android Net Shaman's Hairstyle (Male){N}There's no resisting the gentlemanly elegance of this do's pinkish hue!" />
	<string key="N1011170" ger="Net Shaman Luna M Wild Style" eng="Net Shaman Luna M Style" />
	<string key="T1011170" ger="Security Android Net Shaman's Face (Male)" eng="Security Android Net Shaman's Face (Male)" />
	<string key="N1021170" ger="Net Shaman Luna M Open Vest" eng="Net Shaman Luna M Open Vest" />
	<string key="T1021170" ger="Security Android Net Shaman's Shirt (Male){N}Der einzigartige Schnitt lässt auf außergewöhnliche Qualität dieses Items schließen." eng="Security Android Net Shaman's Shirt (Male){N}The subtle taper at the waistline is a sign of this item's exquisite quality." />
	<string key="N1031170" ger="Net Shaman Luna M Baggy Pants" eng="Net Shaman Luna M Baggy Pants" />
	<string key="T1031170" ger="Security Android Net Shaman's Pants (Male)" eng="Security Android Net Shaman's Pants (Male)" />
	<string key="N1041170" ger="Net Shaman Luna M Gloves" eng="Net Shaman Luna M Gloves" />
	<string key="T1041170" ger="Security Android Net Shaman's Gloves (Male)" eng="Security Android Net Shaman's Gloves (Male)" />
	<string key="N1051170" ger="Net Shaman Luna M Shoes" eng="Net Shaman Luna M Shoes" />
	<string key="T1051170" ger="Security Android Net Shaman's Shoes (Male){N}Die angebrachte Schnalle sieht nicht nur schick aus – sie bietet auch Schutz!" eng="Security Android Net Shaman's Shoes (Male){N}The integrated anklet is more than just decoration - it actually provides added protection!" />
	<string key="N1061170" ger="Net Shaman Luna M Mask" eng="Net Shaman Luna M Mask" />
	<string key="T1061170" ger="Security Android Net Shaman's Mask{N}Auf den ersten Blick scheint der Träger dieser Maske nichts sehen zu können. Glücklicherweise sorgt das eingebaute Display für Sicht, während der Träger gleichzeitig den Rundumschutz einer Maske genießen kann." eng="Security Android Net Shaman's Mask{N}At first glance, you might think the wearer wouldn't be able to see anything. Luckily, the interior display makes it possible to see while enjoying the protection of a closed mask." />
	<string key="N1001171" ger="Net Shaman Luna W Wild Style" eng="Net Shaman Luna W Wild Style" />
	<string key="T1001171" ger="Security Android Net Shaman's Hairstyle (Female)" eng="Security Android Net Shaman's Hairstyle (Female)" />
	<string key="N1011171" ger="Net Shaman Luna W Style" eng="Net Shaman Luna W Style" />
	<string key="T1011171" ger="Security Android Net Shaman's Face (Female)" eng="Security Android Net Shaman's Face (Female)" />
	<string key="N1021171" ger="Net Shaman Luna W Open Vest" eng="Net Shaman Luna W Open Vest" />
	<string key="T1021171" ger="Security Android Net Shaman's Top (Female){N}Dieses Oberteil bietet kaum Schutz, fasziniert aber mit seinem wilden Stil." eng="Security Android Net Shaman's Top (Female){N}This item sacrifices coverage and protection for its wildly stylish cut." />
	<string key="N1031171" ger="Net Shaman Luna W Shorts" eng="Net Shaman Luna W Shorts" />
	<string key="T1031171" ger="Security Android Net Shaman's Pants (Female){N}Nicht so kurz wie die meisten Röcke und super bequem!" eng="Security Android Net Shaman's Pants (Female){N}While these are not quite as short as your typical skirt, they're infinitely more comfortable to move around in!" />
	<string key="N1041171" ger="Net Shaman Luna W Gloves" eng="Net Shaman Luna W Gloves" />
	<string key="T1041171" ger="Security Android Net Shaman's Gloves (Female)" eng="Security Android Net Shaman's Gloves (Female)" />
	<string key="N1051171" ger="Net Shaman Luna W Shoes" eng="Net Shaman Luna W Shoes" />
	<string key="T1051171" ger="Security Android Net Shaman's Shoes (Female)" eng="Security Android Net Shaman's Shoes (Female)" />
	<string key="N1061171" ger="Net Shaman Luna W Mask" eng="Net Shaman Luna W Mask" />
	<string key="T1061171" ger="Security Android Net Shaman's Mask{N}Auf den ersten Blick scheint der Träger dieser Maske nichts sehen zu können. Glücklicherweise sorgt das eingebaute Display für Sicht und der Träger kann gleichzeitig den Rundumschutz dieser Maske genießen." eng="Security Android Net Shaman's Mask{N}At first glance, you might think the wearer wouldn't be able to see anything. Luckily, the interior display makes it possible to see while enjoying the protection of a closed mask." />
	<string key="N1070065" ger="Unformed Flame Pet" eng="Unformed Flame Pet" />
	<string key="T1070065" ger="Security Android Net Shaman's pet.{N}Obwohl es aus einer blauen Flamme besteht, fühlt es sich bei Berührung doch eher kühl an." eng="Security Android Net Shaman's pet.{N}Even though it looks to be made of pure blue flame, this creature is cool to the touch." />
	<string key="N1001172" ger="Martin's Volume Dandy Cut" eng="Martin's Volume Dandy Cut" />
	<string key="T1001172" ger="Passt gut zum eher seriösen Stil und lässt dich trotzdem jung wirken." eng="It goes well with formal attire, with styling that keeps you looking youthful." />
	<string key="N1021172" ger="Martin's Long Blazer" eng="Martin's Long Blazer" />
	<string key="T1021172" ger="Das Jackett ohne Knöpfe sieht mit dem weißen Hemd besonders elegant aus." eng="This buttonless blazer looks even more sophisticated paired with a white shirt." />
	<string key="N1031172" ger="Martin's Skinny Slacks" eng="Martin's Skinny Slacks" />
	<string key="T1031172" ger="Schmale Hosen mit schmalen Streifen." eng="Skinny slacks, patterned with slimming stripes." />
	<string key="N1041172" ger="Martin's Gold Watch" eng="Martin's Gold Watch" />
	<string key="T1041172" ger="Wuchtige Golduhr.{N}Lässt dich allerdings älter aussehen, als du bist." eng="A luxurious gold watch.{N}Wearing it might even make you look a bit sophisticated." />
	<string key="N1051172" ger="Martin's Canvas Boots" eng="Martin's Canvas Boots" />
	<string key="T1051172" ger="Canvas-Stiefel.{N}Der letzte Schrei bei den jungen Herren." eng="Ankle-high boots made of sturdy canvas.{N}A hot item among stylish young gentlemen." />
	<string key="N1021173" ger="Marine Medic Dress Top" eng="Marine Medic Dress Top" />
	<string key="T1021173" ger="Kleidchen im Krankenschwester-Look.{N}Der chinesische Kragen gibt ihm den letzten Schliff." eng="Nurse-style clothing.{N}Its Eastern-looking collar makes it even more unique." />
	<string key="N1031173" ger="Marine Medic Dress Skirt" eng="Marine Medic Dress Skirt" />
	<string key="T1031173" ger="Kleidchen im Krankenschwester-Look.{N}Heißes Röckchen mit züchtigen Kniestrümpfen." eng="Nurse-style clothing.{N}A miniskirt with knee-high socks - this look can't be beat!" />
	<string key="N1041173" ger="Marine's Long Gloves" eng="Marine's Long Gloves" />
	<string key="T1041173" ger="Lange Handschuhe im Look von OP-Handschuhen.{N}Sollten bei Operationen aber besser nicht getragen werden." eng="Long, tight-fitting gloves with a military aesthetic.{N}Can't be worn during operations." />
	<string key="N1051173" ger="Marine Flat Form Pumps" eng="Marine Flat Formal Pumps" />
	<string key="T1051173" ger="Klassische Pumps, die gleichzeitig seriös und verführerisch aussehen." eng="These formal pumps are sure to show off your legs." />
	<string key="N1061173" ger="Marine Nurse Cap" eng="Marine Nurse Cap" />
	<string key="T1061173" ger="Schwesternhaube{N}Die Zöpfe sind das Tüpfelchen auf dem i." eng="A mini-sized nurse cap.{N}Cute pigtails lend it even more charm." />
	<string key="N1001174" ger="Bloody Hunter Cut" eng="Bloody Hunter Cut" />
	<string key="T1001174" ger="Frisur des Bloody Hunter.{N}Zweifarbig mit langem Pony." eng="Bloody Hunter's hair style. {N}Two-toned hair with long bangs." />
	<string key="N1021174" ger="Bloody Hunter Jacket" eng="Bloody Hunter Jacket" />
	<string key="T1021174" ger="Eine Jacke mit einem Siegelmechanismus, um den Teufel und die Höllenflammen auf dem Arm in Schach zu halten." eng="A jacket equipped with a sealing device to suppress the fiery devil within its sleeve." />
	<string key="N1031174" ger="Bloody Hunter Pants" eng="Bloody Hunter Pants" />
	<string key="T1031174" ger="Zerrissene Hosen und ein Gürtel mit Totenkopfschnalle.{N}Handgefertigte Einzelstücke!" eng="A skull-shaped buckle and distressed pants. {N}They appear to have been torn with loving care..." />
	<string key="N1041174" ger="Bloody Hunter Gloves" eng="Bloody Hunter Gloves" />
	<string key="T1041174" ger="Enthalten einen Siegelmechanismus, um den Teufel auf dem Arm in Schach zu halten.{N}Ziehst du die Handschuhe aus, wird der Teufel freigelassen." eng="Devil-suppressing gloves with arcane powers. {N}Do you dare to take them off...?" />
	<string key="N1051174" ger="Bloody Hunter Boots" eng="Bloody Hunter Boots" />
	<string key="T1051174" ger="Stiefel mit einem Sprungboost-Mechanismus." eng="Boots equipped with a device that bolsters your jumping ability." />
	<string key="N1001175" ger="Bloody Huntress Cut" eng="Bloody Huntress Cut" />
	<string key="T1001175" ger="Frisur für die Bloody Huntress.{N}Die Hörner sind beeindruckend." eng="Bloody Huntress's hairstyle. {N}Complete with horns!" />
	<string key="N1021175" ger="Bloody Huntress Jacket" eng="Bloody Huntress Jacket" />
	<string key="T1021175" ger="Die ultimative Kampfjacke der Bloody Huntress." eng="Ultimate Bloody Huntress's Battle Mode" />
	<string key="N1031175" ger="Bloody Huntress Skirt" eng="Bloody Huntress Skirt" />
	<string key="T1031175" ger="Kurzer Rock.{N}Auf dem linken Bein befindet sich ein Mechanismus, um den Teufel zu versiegeln." eng="A short skirt. {N}The left leg has been equipped with a devil-sealing device." />
	<string key="N1041175" ger="Bloody Huntress Gauntlets" eng="Bloody Huntress Gauntlets" />
	<string key="T1041175" ger="Das Design wurde von den Händen des Teufels inspiriert.{N}Sie beinhalten einen Siegelmechanismus für den Teufel." eng="Designed after the devil himself, these gloves contain arcane, devil-sealing powers." />
	<string key="N1051175" ger="Bloody Huntress Shoes" eng="Bloody Huntress Shoes" />
	<string key="T1051175" ger="Diese Schuhe erhöhen die Magie ihrer Trägerin." eng="Shoes designed to increase your magic powers." />
	<string key="N4020091" />
	<string key="T4020091" />
	<string key="N4020092" />
	<string key="T4020092" />
	<string key="N4020093" />
	<string key="T4020093" />
	<string key="N4020094" />
	<string key="T4020094" />
	<string key="N4020095" ger="Random Weapon Capsule" eng="Random Weapon Capsule" />
	<string key="T4020095" ger="Die Kapsel enthält eine seltene Waffe.{N}Bei Benutzung erhältst du eine zufällige Waffe." eng="A capsule containing a rare weapon.{N}When used, you'll acquire 1 random weapon." />
	<string key="N4020096" ger="Random Costume Capsule" eng="Random Costume Capsule" />
	<string key="T4020096" ger="Die Kapsel enthält ein seltenes Kostüm.{N}Bei Benutzung erhältst du ein zufälliges Kostüm.{N}Zufallskostüme werden ohne Rücksicht auf das Geschlecht des Charakters vergeben. " eng="A capsule containing a rare costume.{N}When used, you'll acquire 1 random costume.{N}Random costumes will be awarded regardless of character's gender. " />
	<string key="N4020097" ger="Wonderful Weapon Box" eng="Wonderful Weapon Box" />
	<string key="T4020097" ger="In dieser Box steckt eine großartige Waffe.{N}Nach dem Öffnen erhältst du eine zufällige Waffe (Permanent)." eng="A box containing a wonderful weapon.{N}When opened, you'll acquire 1 random Permanent weapon." />
	<string key="N4020098" ger="Wonderful Costume Box" eng="Wonderful Costume Box" />
	<string key="T4020098" ger="In dieser Box steckt ein großartiges Kostüm.{N}Nach dem Öffnen erhältst du ein zufälliges Kostüm (Permanent)." eng="A box containing a wonderful costume.{N}When opened, you'll acquire 1 random Permanent costume." />
	<string key="N4020099" />
	<string key="T4020099" />
	<string key="N4020100" ger="Blueberry" eng="Blueberry" />
	<string key="N4020101" ger="Apple" eng="Apple" />
	<string key="N4020102" ger="Plum" eng="Plum" />
	<string key="N4020103" ger="Grape" eng="Grape" />
	<string key="N4020104" ger="Lychee" eng="Lychee" />
	<string key="N4020105" ger="Banana" eng="Banana" />
	<string key="T4020100" ger="Small like the blueberry, this box will get you those tiny things you're missing" eng="Small like the blueberry, this box will get you those tiny things you're missing" />
	<string key="T4020101" ger="Like the apple, one of these a day will keep the doctor away and will give you all you need." eng="Like the apple, one of these a day will keep the doctor away and will give you all you need." />
	<string key="T4020102" ger="Give your face a lift with the power of the plum box!" eng="Give your face a lift with the power of the plum box!" />
	<string key="T4020103" ger="Mastering the grape box will give you all the skills you need to achieve grapeness." eng="Mastering the grape box will give you all the skills you need to achieve grapeness." />
	<string key="T4020104" ger="Get through the hard skin of the Lychee box and grab the sweet perm's inside." eng="Get through the hard skin of the Lychee box and grab the sweet perm's inside." />
	<string key="T4020105" ger="Peel it and open up the best box of our summer event!" eng="Peel it and open up the best box of our summer event!" />
	<string key="N6000038" ger="Summer Token" eng="Summer Token" />
	<string key="T6000038" ger="Collect these Summer Tokens to exchange for various Event Boxes." eng="Collect these Summer Tokens to exchange for various Event Boxes." />
	<string key="N4035238" ger="Shark Saviour Set (Permanent)" eng="Shark Savior Set (Permanent)" />
	<string key="T4035238" ger="Shark Saviour Set. {N}Set beinhaltet folgende Items:" eng="Shark Savior Set. {N}The set contains the following items" />
	<string key="N4051477" ger="Shark Slayer Set (Permanent)" eng="Shark Slayer Set (Permanent)" />
	<string key="T4051477" ger="Shark Slayer Set. {N}Set beinhaltet folgende Items:" eng="Shark Slayer Set. {N}The set contains the following items" />
	<string key="N2000055" ger="Virtual Shield" eng="Virtual Shield" />
	<string key="T2000055" ger="Net Shaman Luna's exclusive Counter Sword.{N}Diese einzigartige Waffe, wurde in Lunas Testphase entwickelt.{N}Sie ist sowohl als Offensiv- als auch als Defensivwaffe bestens geeignet.{N}Gewinner des EU Community Workshop: Krayds" eng="Net Shaman Luna's exclusive Counter Sword.{N}This unique weapon was developed during Luna's test phase.{N}With the ability to switch freely between offensive and defensive modes, it's an extremely effective and flexible weapon.{N}Winner of the EU Community Workshop contest: Krayds" />
	<string key="N3020004" ger="Virtual Wing" eng="Virtual Wing" />
	<string key="T3020004" ger="Net Shaman Luna's exclusive Virtual Wing.{N}Diese einzigartige Ausrüstung wurde in Lunas Testphase entwickelt.{N}Es ist den Schwingen eines Adlers nachempfunden und kann platzsparend zusammengefaltet werden." eng="Net Shaman Luna's exclusive Virtual Wing.{N}This unique equipment was developed during Luna's test phase.{N}Fashioned after a set of eagle's wings, it was designed to fold for easy storage." />
	<string key="N4035374" ger="G's Virtual Shield Capsule" eng="G's Virtual Shield Capsule" />
