	<string key="N2000063" ger="Vital Shock" eng="Vital Shock" />
	<string key="T2000063" ger="Versiegelt in den Tiefen der Netsphere, ruhte diese tödliche Nahkampfwaffe.{N}Uz, dem Netsphere-Entwickler, gelang ein noch besseres Re-Design. Mr. J und Mr. B. halfen ihm dabei. " eng="This lethal melee weapon was sealed deep inside the Netsphere.{N}A prototype version was uncovered, and the Netsphere developer, Uz, was able to redesign and upgrade it with help of Mr. J and Mr. B. " />
