	<string key="N4170002" ger="Lucky eSper 100" eng="Lucky eSper 100" />
	<string key="T4170002" ger="Mit diesem Item verzauberst du eSper-Chips zu 100%. Kann auf der Enchant-Seite für eSper-Chips benutzt werden." eng="Guarantees eSper Chip enhancement. Can be used from the eSper Chip Enchant page." />
	<string key="N4180001" ger="eSper Insurance" eng="eSper Insurance" />
	<string key="T4180001" ger="Das Item schützt bei der eSper-Chip-Verzauberung vor Zerstörung. Kann auf der Enchant-Seite für eSper-Chips benutzt werden." eng="Counteracts failure of eSper Chip enhancement. Can be used in the eSper Chip Enchant page." />
	<string key="N1061188" ger="Marsh Feline Helmet" eng="Marsh Feline Helmet" />
	<string key="T1061188" ger="Es juckt voll darunter. Darf ich ihn absetzen? Miau?" eng="It looks great, doesn't it? It's a little itchy, though... The things we do for fashion, huh?" />
	<string key="N1021188" ger="Marsh Feline Tights Top" eng="Marsh Feline Tights Top" />
	<string key="T1021188" ger="Ich schwitze mich tot! Darf ich mich ausziehen? Miau?" eng="How do I look? Do I look hot? Because I feel like I'm roasting in this thing..." />
	<string key="N1031188" ger="Marsh Feline Tights Bottom" eng="Marsh Feline Tights Bottom" />
	<string key="T1031188" ger="Total unbequem! Echt ... Miau!" eng="They're not all that comfortable, but sometimes fashion comes at a purr-ice!" />
	<string key="N1041188" ger="Marsh Feline Gloves" eng="Marsh Feline Gloves" />
	<string key="T1041188" ger="Tut's mit den Handschuhen mehr weh? Miau?" eng="Let's hope these gloves hurt your enemies more than they hurt you. Me-ouch!" />
	<string key="N1051188" ger="Marsh Feline Shoes" eng="Marsh Feline Shoes" />
	<string key="T1051188" ger="Was ist denn los? Miau?" eng="What are mew looking at? This furry footwear is purrfect!" />
	<string key="N1061189" ger="Mallow Feline Helmet" eng="Mallow Feline Helmet" />
	<string key="T1061189" ger="Kommst du auch aus dem Universum? Miau?" eng="This cat hat is out of this world! It'll be tough to get enough of strutting your stuff!" />
	<string key="N1021189" ger="Mallow Feline Leotard Top" eng="Mallow Feline Leotard Top" />
	<string key="T1021189" ger="Knall mich ins All! Miau!" eng="Want to avoid a fashion cat-astrophe? This top is tabby-chic!" />
	<string key="N1031189" ger="Mallow Feline Leotard Bottom" eng="Mallow Feline Leotard Bottom" />
	<string key="T1031189" ger="Willst du das auch mal anziehen? Miau? Passt fast, haha. Miau ..." eng="Nothing quite like some fine feline fur to freshen up your fashion! Never mind that they're insanely uncomfortable— these bottoms are tops!" />
	<string key="N1041189" ger="Mallow Feline Gloves" eng="Mallow Feline Gloves" />
	<string key="T1041189" ger="Super süß, oder? Miau ..." eng="Aren't they cute? They make it a little difficult to pick things up..." />
	<string key="N1051189" ger="Mallow Feline Shoes" eng="Mallow Feline Shoes" />
	<string key="T1051189" ger="Extrem bequem! Kennst du die? Miau ..." eng="They're so soft... I can move around almost silently! They would be purrfect for sneak attacks..." />
	<string key="N2000064" ger="Curious Cat Claw" eng="Curious Cat Claw" />
	<string key="T2000064" ger="Neugier ist der Katze Tod? Miau ...{N}Die Waffe verspricht eines garantiert: Mit einem Knall ist der Feind im All! Miau ..." eng="Curiosity killed the cat, huh? Well, these claws are just as deadly!{N}If you're looking for a great new way to shred your foes to ribbons, look no further. These claws will earn you applause!" />
	<string key="N1070078" ger="Nyan Fumbi" eng="Nyan Fumbi" />
	<string key="T1070078" ger="Ich bin Nyan Fumbi." eng="I am Nyan Fumbi!" />
