	<string key="N4052203" ger="Faux Seaweed" eng="Faux Seaweed" />
	<string key="T4052203" ger="Ich dachte, es wäre Seetang – dabei ist es nur ein lumpiges Stück Papier.{N}Nein, es ist NICHT essbar." eng="Looks exactly like seaweed, but it's actually made of paper.{N}It's not edible. Don't ask me how I know." />
	<string key="N4052204" ger="Toy Fish" eng="Toy Fish" />
	<string key="T4052204" ger="Kennst du das Magnet-Angelspiel?{N}Da kommt der Fisch her." eng="This faux fish was picked up with a magnet. {N} I wonder who threw it away..." />
	<string key="N4052205" ger="Starfish" eng="Starfish" />
	<string key="T4052205" ger="Auf diesen Sonderling haben es Marsh und Mallow abgesehen.{N}Wieso? Das steht in den Sternen!" eng="Marsh and Mallow are both enthralled with this water-breather.{N}I'm not convinced... I guess we'll have to agree to disagree." />
	<string key="N4052206" ger="Scrumptious Crab " eng="Scrumptious Crab" />
	<string key="T4052206" ger="Wow! Dieses Teil schmeckt fantastisch!" eng="Delicious! This is the best crab you'll eat all year." />
	<string key="N4052207" ger="Gilded Turtle" eng="Gilded Turtle" />
	<string key="T4052207" ger="Eine solche Schildkröte wird nur ein Mal alle 1000 Jahre geboren.{N}Was für'n Glück." eng="This armored reptile glitters with gold and only appears every thousand years.{N}Who can possibly resist its charms?" />
	<string key="N4020159" ger="Water" eng="Water" />
	<string key="T4020159" ger="Like water, the most important thing for spring!" eng="Like water, the most important thing for spring!" />
	<string key="N4020160" ger="Grass" eng="Grass" />
	<string key="T4020160" ger="The grass is growing and the rabbits are coming out. Grab yours before it runs away!" eng="The grass is growing and the rabbits are coming out. Grab yours before it runs away!" />
	<string key="N4020161" ger="Blossom" eng="Blossom" />
	<string key="T4020161" ger="Spring is colorful and vibrant. Get a new look for this spring! Female Pen version." eng="Spring is colorful and vibrant. Get a new look for this spring! Female Pen version." />
	<string key="N4020162" ger="Sakura" eng="Sakura" />
	<string key="T4020162" ger="Spring is colorful and vibrant. Get a new look for this spring! Male Pen version." eng="Spring is colorful and vibrant. Get a new look for this spring! Male Pen version." />
	<string key="N4020163" ger="Rabbit" eng="Rabbit" />
	<string key="T4020163" ger="Easter is around and the rabbit has brought some great items! Female AP version. " eng="Easter is around and the rabbit has brought some great items! Female AP version. " />
	<string key="N4020164" ger="Egg" eng="Egg" />
	<string key="T4020164" ger="Easter is around and the rabbit has brought some great items! Male AP version. " eng="Easter is around and the rabbit has brought some great items! Male AP version. " />
	<string key="N4052208" eng="Blue Wave" />
	<string key="T4052208" eng="Calm waters, can change you to a great tsunami!" />
	<string key="N4052209" eng="Green Seaweed" />
	<string key="T4052209" eng="Contains nutrients that can enhance both you and your equipment!" />
	<string key="N4052210" eng="Purple Dawn" />
	<string key="T4052210" eng="When the night is dark, you will be a star!" />
	<string key="N4052211" eng="Violet Dusk" />
	<string key="T4052211" eng="Light up the morning, with your presence!" />
	<string key="N4052212" eng="Silver Stream" />
	<string key="T4052212" eng="This box could not even contain the hotness of this summer set!" />
	<string key="N4052213" eng="Golden Sand" />
	<string key="T4052213" eng="Peel it and open up the best box of our summer event!" />
