	<string key="N1061192" ger="Davy's Sailor Beret" eng="Davy's Sailor Beret" />
	<string key="T1061192" ger="Eine Baskenmütze der Netsphere-Matrosen.{N}Nicht praktisch, aber ziemlich cool!" eng="A beret worn by Netsphere sailors.{N}It's not practical, but at least it looks cool!" />
	<string key="N1021192" ger="Davy's Sailor Jacket " eng="Davy's Sailor Jacket " />
	<string key="T1021192" ger="Teil der männlichen Netsphere-Matrosen-Uniform.{N}Putze dich mit dieser eleganten Jacke heraus und setz die Segel für ein neues Abenteuer!" eng="Part of a uniform worn by male Netsphere sailors.{N}Deck yourself out in these dapper duds and set sail for a high-seas adventure!" />
	<string key="N1031192" ger="Davy's Sailor Pants" eng="Davy's Sailor Pants" />
	<string key="T1031192" ger="Teil der männlichen Netsphere-Matrosen-Uniform.{N}Diese Hosen sind für das Leben auf dem Meer perfekt geeignet." eng="Part of a uniform worn by male Netsphere sailors.{N}Its bright, fade-resistant fabric is well suited to the salty sea air." />
	<string key="N1041192" ger="Davy's Sailor Gloves" eng="Davy's Sailor Gloves" />
	<string key="T1041192" ger="Ein Paar Handschuhe männlicher Netsphere-Matrosen." eng="A pair of gloves worn by male Netsphere sailors." />
	<string key="N1051192" ger="Davy's Sailor Shoes" eng="Davy's Sailor Shoes" />
	<string key="T1051192" ger="Wasserdichte Schuhe der männlichen Netsphere-Matrosen.{N}Das einzigartige, nautische Design macht sie zu einem Hit für Jung und Alt." eng="A pair of waterproof shoes worn by male Netsphere sailors{N}Its unique, nautical design makes it a popular choice for young and old salts alike." />
	<string key="N1061193" ger="Nautica's Sailor Hat" eng="Nautica's Sailor Hat" />
	<string key="T1061193" ger="Der Hut der weiblichen Netsphere-Matrosen.{N}Simpel, aber dadurch umso eleganter!" eng="A hat worn by female Netsphere sailors.{N}Its elegant simplicity leaves room for further accessorizing, making it a popular summer choice." />
	<string key="N1021193" ger="Nautica's Sailor Top" eng="Nautica's Sailor Top" />
	<string key="T1021193" ger="Ein hübsches Top, wie es weibliche Netsphere-Matrosen tragen." eng="A cute, custom top worn by female Netsphere sailors." />
	<string key="N1031193" ger="Nautica's Sailor Shorts" eng="Nautica's Sailor Shorts" />
	<string key="T1031193" ger="Diese Shorts sind perfekt für den Sommer!{N}Sie kommen außerdem mit einem extra Strumpfband daher." eng="These shorts are a favorite choice for ladies lounging about on hot summer days.{N} Plus, it comes with a bonus thigh accessory that pushes cuteness to the limit!" />
	<string key="N1041193" ger="Nautica's Sailor Gloves" eng="Nautica's Sailor Gloves" />
	<string key="T1041193" ger="Ein Paar Halbhandschuhe. Die sind in der Netsphere besonders beliebt.{N}Sie gewähren volle Bewegungsfreiheit  und büßen dabei nicht an Stil ein!" eng="A pair of open-finger gloves popular in the Netsphere.{N}Its unique design protects the hands while granting freedom of motion, a necessity on the high seas. Plus, it makes the wearer both look and feel cool!" />
	<string key="N1051193" ger="Nautica's Sailor Shoes" eng="Nautica's Sailor Shoes" />
	<string key="T1051193" ger="Ein Paar wasserdichter Schuhe. Sie erinnern an jene, die man früher in der Marine getragen hat." eng="A pair of trendy waterproof shoes with a design inspired by traditional navy footwear." />
