	<string key="N1011210" ger="Vlad's Face" eng="Vlad's Face" />
	<string key="T1011210" ger="Vampirgesicht mit Blut an den Lippen." eng="A vampire face with blood dripping from its mouth." />
	<string key="N1021210" ger="Vlad's Coat" eng="Vlad's Coat" />
	<string key="T1021210" ger="Edler Mantel für den galanten Auftritt auf jeder Halloweenparty." eng="The coat of a mysterious nobleman who came to the Halloween party." />
	<string key="N1031210" ger="Vlad's Pants" eng="Vlad's Pants" />
	<string key="T1031210" ger="Edle Hose für den galanten Auftritt auf jeder Halloweenparty." eng="The pants of a mysterious nobleman who came to the Halloween party." />
