	<string key="N4052366" ger="2016 Christmas Event Capsule" eng="2016 Christmas Event Capsule" />
	<string key="T4052366" ger="Ein Weihnachtsgeschenk für euch! Ratet mal, was drin ist!" eng="Christmas Present for you! Guess what is inside!" />
	<string key="N1021225" ger="Winter Spirit Skate Suit" eng="Winter Spirit Skate Suit" />
	<string key="T1021225" ger="Mit dieser Jacke macht man auf jeder Eisbahn eine gute Figur." eng="A jacket designed to rock the ice ring." />
	<string key="N1031225" ger="Winter Spirit Skate Pants" eng="Winter Spirit Skate Pants" />
	<string key="T1031225" ger="Diese Hosen halten sogar den eisigsten Frost ab." eng="These pants can keep you warm in the coldest winters." />
	<string key="N1041225" ger="Winter Spirit Gloves" eng="Winter Spirit Gloves" />
	<string key="T1041225" ger="{CB-255,255,0,255}[Safety First]{N}{CB-255,255,255,255} Mit diesen Handschuhen sind eure Finger vor Angriffen bösartiger Kufen geschützt." eng="{CB-255,255,0,255}[Safety First]{N}{CB-255,255,255,255} These gloves will protect you from injuries on the ice ring." />
